OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202756
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FThousands of people in Hawaii have
OL,8,Fbeen urged to evacuate after the state
OL,9,Fexperienced its worst flooding in more
OL,10,Fthan 20 years.
OL,12,FHeavy rain fell on soil already
OL,13,Fsaturated by downpours from a winter
OL,14,Fstorm one week ago, sending muddy
OL,15,Ffloodwaters stretching over vast
OL,16,Fswathes of Oahu's North Shore.
OL,18,FWith more flooding expected over the
OL,19,Fweekend, evacuation orders for 5,500
OL,20,Fpeople north of Honolulu was issued on
OL,21,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202756
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FAlthough they were later lifted,
OL,8,Fauthorities have warned that flooding
OL,9,Fcould lead to the failure of a 120-
OL,10,Fyear-old dam that has been vulnerable
OL,11,Ffor decades.
OL,13,FHawaii officials say the Wahiawa dam
OL,14,Fis "at risk of imminent failure" and
OL,15,Fhas "high hazard potential", adding
OL,16,Fthat a failure "will result in
OL,17,Fprobable loss of human life".
OL,26,@vD@DOUvD@`O]wD@EOUwD@[O]xD@POUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202757
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FWater levels in the dam about 17 miles
OL,8,Fnorthwest of Honolulu, on the island
OL,9,Fof Oahu, receded by late Friday and
OL,10,Fthen went up again with overnight rain.
OL,12,FHowever the dam appeared to be less of
OL,13,Fa concern the following morning than
OL,14,Fthe "breadth of hazardous conditions"
OL,15,Facross the island, said Molly Pierce,
OL,16,Fa spokesperson for Oahu's Department
OL,17,Fof Emergency Management.
OL,19,FShe noted substantial flooding
OL,20,Fincluding in residential parts of
OL,21,FHonolulu.
OL,26,@vD@EOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202757
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,F"We're seeing the waters receding in a
OL,8,Flot of places, but again with that
OL,9,Fsaturation, just the smallest amount
OL,10,Fof water can bring those raging back
OL,11,Fup," Ms Pierce said.
OL,13,F"So even if it's blue skies where you
OL,14,Fare, I think we all know in Hawaii
OL,15,Fthat if rain is falling on the
OL,16,Fmountain, it's coming to you soon
OL,17,Fenough."
OL,19,FKathleen Pahinui evacuated her Waialua
OL,20,Fhome early Friday because of the
OL,21,Fdanger posed by the dam.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@DO]uD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202757
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,F"Hopefully if we make it through
OL,8,Ftoday, then tomorrow will dawn bright
OL,9,Fand sunny," she said on Saturday. "And
OL,10,Fthen everyone can start moving slowly
OL,11,Fback in, and we can start to resume
OL,12,Fnormal and start cleaning up and
OL,13,Fhelping our neighbours."
OL,15,FOn the island of Maui, authorities
OL,16,Fupgraded an evacuation advisory to a
OL,17,Fwarning for some parts of Lahaina,
OL,18,Fwhich is still reeling from a deadly
OL,19,F2023 wildfire, because of retention
OL,20,Fbasins nearing capacity.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@KO]qD@cOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202757
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FNorth Shore Oahu residents who did not
OL,8,Fevacuate were heartened in the morning
OL,9,Fby receding waters and moments of blue
OL,10,Fskies, but more rain was on the way.
OL,12,F"Don't let your guard down just yet,"
OL,13,Fsaid Tina Stall, a meteorologist with
OL,14,Fthe National Weather Service in
OL,15,FHonolulu, "there's still potential for
OL,16,Fmore flooding impacts."
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@eO]wD@KOUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202757
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FGovernor Josh Green said the cost of
OL,8,Fthe storm could top $1 billion (around
OL,9,F#750 million), including damage to
OL,10,Fairports, schools, roads, homes and a
OL,11,FMaui hospital in Kula.
OL,13,F"This is going to have a very serious
OL,14,Fconsequence for us as a state," he
OL,15,Ftold a a news conference. He also said
OL,16,Fhis chief of staff spoke to the White
OL,17,FHouse and received assurances of
OL,18,Ffederal support.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202757
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FGreen said the flooding was the
OL,8,Fstate's most serious since 2004, when
OL,9,Fhomes and a University of Hawaii
OL,10,Flibrary were swamped.
OL,12,FOfficials blamed some of the
OL,13,Fdevastation on the sheer amount of
OL,14,Frain that fell in a short amount of
OL,15,Ftime on saturated land. Parts of Oahu
OL,16,Freceived 8 to 12 inches, the National
OL,17,FWeather Service said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202757
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FMore than 200 people were rescued from
OL,8,Fthe rising waters, authorities said,
OL,9,Fbut no deaths were reported and no one
OL,10,Fwas unaccounted for. Crews searched by
OL,11,Fair and by water for stranded people.
OL,13,FThe National Guard and Honolulu Fire
OL,14,FDepartment airlifted 72 children and
OL,15,Fadults from a spring break youth camp
OL,16,Fat a retreat on Oahu's west coast
OL,17,Fcalled Our Lady of Kea'au, city
OL,18,Fofficials said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774202757
OL,3,CHawaii suffers worst flooding in 20
OL,4,Cyears as dam 'at risk of imminent
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FThe camp is on high ground, but
OL,8,Fauthorities did not want to leave them
OL,9,Fthere, the mayor said.
OL,11,FWinter storm systems known as "Kona
OL,12,Flows," which feature southerly or
OL,13,Fsouthwesterly winds that bring in
OL,14,Fmoisture-laden air, have been
OL,15,Fresponsible for the deluges in the
OL,16,Fpast two weeks.
OL,18,FThe intensity and frequency of heavy
OL,19,Frains in Hawaii have increased amid
OL,20,Fhuman-caused global warming, experts
OL,21,Fsay.
OL,26,@sD@_OUtD@FO]
